“de_veranda_bobpoblo”

After many requests to turn my fy/gg_Veranda maps into a Bomb/ Defuse version, here it is!

This is a medium sized, symmetrical Bomb/ Defuse style map. If you’ve played my other veranda maps then you will love this one! HFGL

- 64 Spawns
- 3d skybox
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Overview radar map
- Buy Zones
- Nav File for bots
- Pakrated
